{"tid":1428696,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(文宣做野) 證物必須放在證物室,並用證物袋密封包住","createTime":"2019-08-07T10:41:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T12:59:05.000Z","uid":222970,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"eb8f436fa2c73313d939beafd544ba042a274a9e","tid":1428696,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:41:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NOR7DG2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNOR7DG2.png&h=03a75d31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/200804/16/P200804160222.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F200804%2F16%2FP200804160222.htm&d=%2BDaDB54%2FKEfuO7Vsi8VjQ%2FBNkMLqpq56k8mIdjvCyJE%3D&h=21197b40\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/200804/16/P200804160222.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n立法會十四題：警方按劃一程序處理證物<br />\n<br />\n（二）警方如何保管以電子形式儲存的證物，以及有否指派人員負責看管這些證物，防止任何人擅自接觸證物；若有，詳情為何；<br />\n<br />\n（二）至（四）警方按劃一程序處理各類型的證物（包括以電子形式儲存的證物）。<span style=\"color: red;\">警務人員在進行調查時如檢獲任何證物，須交予所屬警署內專責處理證物的人員進行記錄及封存，並妥為保管。</span>只有獲授權人員或處理有關案件的人員方可領取證物，以便跟進調查、上庭、作鑑證測試等指定用途。領取及交還證物的原因以及負責的有關人員的詳細資料，均須予以記錄。"},{"pid":"e319ee079258813e1dbe005924ac1ff32a271b6a","tid":1428696,"uid":222970,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:41:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20180407/mobile/odn-20180407-0407_00176_070.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180407%2Fmobile%2Fodn-20180407-0407_00176_070.html&d=%2BDaDB54%2FKEfuO7Vsi8VjQ%2FBNkMLqpq56k8mIdjvCyJE%3D&h=5904dff3\" target=\"_blank\">https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20180407/mobile/odn-20180407-0407_00176_070.html</a><br />\n<br />\n警員不當處理證物疑犯脫罪"},{"pid":"a93a50967e92809d028dcaa1ad388b7fb7b67d2e","tid":1428696,"uid":222970,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:43:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.ipcc.gov.hk/doc/en/pr/issue23_2018/cover_story.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ipcc.gov.hk%2Fdoc%2Fen%2Fpr%2Fissue23_2018%2Fcover_story.pdf&d=%2BDaDB54%2FKEfuO7Vsi8VjQ%2FBNkMLqpq56k8mIdjvCyJE%3D&h=fbb42ba9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ipcc.gov.hk/doc/en/pr/issue23_2018/cover_story.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n有關證物處理的投訴個案"},{"pid":"0533282cb7ec477a2765cf1ae646af3ccd51aee6","tid":1428696,"uid":28970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:43:09.000Z","msg":"咁撚近就收皮啦黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 就算到實戰都冇可能咁近企定定啦"},{"pid":"28b34053b63f639b7088ea8846bbf2e2c3b9e67b","tid":1428696,"uid":103325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:46:10.000Z","msg":"如果個包頭入邊有錢，佢地可以開包頭攞出嚟用？"},{"pid":"8f2657deb780128be5f76bad205b0ef170164892","tid":1428696,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T11:02:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea06aee6cc39802efd0d37bf94b42c84402c0bfe","tid":1428696,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T11:06:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e3017985590715272c2e02df4303e26e8120131","tid":1428696,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T11:12:14.000Z","msg":"推比記者聽日問"},{"pid":"fdcab177b1ee586111bce179cb4a14d7341b659c","tid":1428696,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T11:22:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41673a67f276e8db124e3e6ee47647aa126179ef","tid":1428696,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T11:25:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c334410eaf30e8c89051f75ffb0135d9e2bf981c","tid":1428696,"u